properties.Name: RefineryTestMethod
properties.Description:
A type of refinery test method.

Ex:

Test                  Test for
----------------------------------------
ASTM D1298, ASTM D4052, IP 365     Density
ASTM D6417     Volatility
ASTM D1401     Water Separability:
ASTM D611     Aniline Point
ASTM D664     Acid Number
ASTM D974     Acid and Base Number
ASTM D130      Copper Strip Corrosion
ASTM D482     Ash Content
ASTM D1218      Refractive Index
ASTM D97, ASTM D5950,ASTM  D5985,ASTM  D5949     Pour Point
ASTM D445, IP 71      Kinematic Viscosity
ASTM D2270, IP 226      Viscosity Index
ASTM D2622, D4294      Sulfur
ASTM D92, D93     Flash Point          
ASTM D1500, D6045     Color
ASTM D2887     Boiling Point Distribution
ASTM D5762     Nitrogen
ASTM D5293     Viscosity by Cold Crank Simulator

ASTM = ASTM International
